{
    "_comment": "Manufacturer-direct datasheet URL patterns. Used by DatasheetUrlResolver as a fallback when no distributor provided a datasheet URL or the chosen URL failed. Placeholders: {mpn}, {mpn_lower}, {mpn_upper}. Manufacturer matching is case-insensitive + whitespace-collapsed against ManufacturerAlias-canonical name + the listed aliases.",

